War of the Worlds;;42;;75;;PG-13;;Dockworker Ray Ferrier (Tom Cruise) struggles to build a positive relationship with his two children, Rachel (Dakota Fanning) and Robbie (Justin Chatwin). When his ex-wife, Mary Ann (Miranda Otto), drops them off at Ferrier's house, it seems as though it will be just another tension-filled weekend. However, when electromagnetic pulses of lightning strike the area, the strange event turns out to be the beginning of an alien invasion, and Ferrier must now protect his children as they seek refuge.;;Action,Adventure,Sci-fi;;Steven Spielberg;;2005;;Tom Cruise,Dakota Fanning,Miranda Otto,Justin Chatwin,Tim Robbins,Rick Gonzalez,Yul Vazquez,Lenny Venito,Lisa Ann Walter,Ann Robinson,Gene Barry,Morgan Freeman,David Alan Basche,James DuMont,Daniel Franzese,Travis Aaron Wade,Ambi Daniel,Mariann Mayberry;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/war_of_the_worlds